Here I was too much in a hurry.  I was planning to promote while neglecting the defence of my King.
Engine says this is a blunder which gives black a checkmate in 7:
34. c7 h4 35. Qg8+ Kxg8 36. c8=Q+ Kg7 37. Qb7+ Rxb7 38. Nc1 Qxc1 39. c4 Rb1 40. g3 Rb2#

34. Qc5 would still make this a game worth playing.
